snippet.title: Season 14: Hazard Official Trailer | Overwatch 2
snippet.description:
Rebel against the ordinary in Season 14: Hazard

Step into the fray with our rebellious new hero, Hazard. This brawl dive Tank is a disruptor unlike any other with high mobility, and a unique blend of offensive and defensive capabilities that he uses to fight for the greater good.

Forge your path to glory with the Season 14 Premium Battle Pass, featuring tons of new cosmetics and 80 Mythic Prisms that you can use to unlock Mythic Thor Reinhardt.

Revisit the roots of Overwatch with the 6v6 Role Queue experiment, bringing back the structured 2-2-2 team composition for a limited time.

Enjoy the return of Winter Wonderland, Overwatch: Classic - Moth Meta, Lunar New Year, and exciting new surprises along the way!

Dive into the chaos when Overwatch 2 Season 14: Hazard arrives Dec 10.

Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC!
